<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>元朗唔簽希堅奴，簽祖連奴大敗筆<br />\n無中鋒唔得，而祖連奴連垃垃都唔要<br />\n放走光頭仔無簽另一個本地防中又係唔好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n元朗都無欲無求啦 降班又未輪到佢 洗乜簽d勁人</blockquote><br />\n問題係上季咁驚喜，呢季嘅落差真係......其實冇光頭同希堅奴嘅影響唔係吹到咁大，今季失嘅波大部份都係死球，而把握力差喺上季有希堅奴時亦唔見得好好多，反擊其實今季係做到好多，但冇埋門一腳，中下遊球隊更加應該要好好練嘅死球戰術又差先係致命傷。曾蛇唔識教死球嘅弱點今季一下子爆出嚟亦係我始料不及。</blockquote><br />\n其實魯斯安奴走左 高空波出晒事</blockquote><br />\n以前成日屌盧思安奴亂標波，結果今季換個杜馬斯又搞到冇人頂波"},{"pid":"3174a3655c5f5e00755af1bdc327613e4cf83617","tid":477131,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd716c87b56f6260e5564f29dcbe78556d8b3cb","tid":477131,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"惟一安慰係黃炎堃比預期穩"},{"pid":"51e917a419bb9c8d2ae8015e7d6b651afa56a488","tid":477131,"uid":75615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T17:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6326a53ba80fbddbd06d22b85d555375ef76ea32","tid":477131,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:03:31.000Z","msg":"笑死，風紀們自己開咗post啦一定係"},{"pid":"6d391b07b292386f3ed5d9a6d489472119412c78","tid":477131,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:11:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8eee012dbf6bfd454571c95b1a59f85148828895","tid":477131,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似有4個post</blockquote><br />\n風紀隊長玩圍威喂嘛"},{"pid":"3848543601fef4779c67fb1f4a7d711169ae59cd","tid":477131,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T07:47:25.000Z","msg":"風紀隊長識啲frd唔係賤種就弱智，近朱者赤，近墨者黑，唉"}]}